            <div type="transcript" id="F320A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>There's a certain Slant of light,</l>
                    <l>Winter Afternoons - </l>
                    <l>That oppresses, like the Heft </l>
                    <l>Of Cathedral Tunes - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Heavenly Hurt, it gives us -</l>
                    <l>We can find no scar, </l>
                    <l>But internal difference - </l>
                    <l>Where the Meanings, are - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>None may teach it - Any - </l>
                    <l>'Tis the Seal Despair -</l>
                    <l>An imperial affliction </l>
                    <l>Sent us of the Air - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>When it comes, the Landscape listens - </l>
                    <l>Shadows - hold their breath - </l>
                    <l>When it goes, 'tis like the Distance</l>
                    <l>On the look of Death - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
